---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 308
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Divine Imprint in Manifestation
  - 66
By: Hermes
---
There is a lamentable departure of divinity from man, when nothing
worthy of heaven, or celestial concerns, is heard or believed, and
when every divine voice is by a necessary silence dumb.
